<HL>
   Forest Products,
   Paper Industry
   Expects Losses
   ---
   Prices for Key Products Slip,
   Demand Remains Soft;
   Hoping for the Bottom
   ----
   By G. Pierre Goad
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
10/11/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B8C
</SO>
<CO>
   BCC BOW GP
</CO>
